Set the current working directory to ./src/, and invoke the command

[path_to_clang_gcc_or_similar] ./nightVM.c ./libnightVM.c -o /usr/local/bin/nightVM -Wall -Wextra -Wno-unused -std=c11 -ldl -lm

To check if nightVM is present in /usr/local/bin/, you can invoke

/usr/local/bin/nightVM --about

which should display some information about nightVM.
